<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>패배</title>
    <link href="/css/lose.css" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body>
    <div class="end-container">
        <h1 class="lose-title">아쉽습니다! 😢</h1>
        <h2 style="color:#ff4d4f; margin-bottom:1.5rem;">스무고개 게임에서 패배하셨습니다.</h2>
        <div class="my-record">
            <h3>나의 기록</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>이름: <span id="my-name"><%= name %></span></li>
                <li>걸린 시간: <span id="my-time"><%= time %></span></li>
                <li>시도 횟수: <span id="my-count"><%= count %></span></li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <button onclick="location.href='/'" class="btn btn-outline-info">홈으로</button>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
